“Some people walk into your life and become your home.
Kunal, you’ve been my rock — through every high and low, every fight, every meltdown. While I grip, shout, overthink, and crumble… you simply stay. Calm. Steady. Listening. Holding space.
I truly don’t know what I would’ve done without you.
Waheguruji has been so kind to bless me with a partner like you — one who loves without noise, supports without conditions, and stays through it all.
If I ever get to be born again, I would still want to be your wife — in every lifetime.
Forever your better half, trying to be better every day. 🤍”
